history.content:
My friend had a similar problem for 16a - she dropped and readded the class but made sure to not click "waitlist if class is full" and then it worked.

If you don't want to try that, the next best bet would be to email cs-enrollments@eecs.berkeley.edu

Hi! Now that it is adjustment period, we should be able to directly enroll in cs170, regardless of declaration status right? The website shows that there are 52 unreserved seat for 170, but there are still 69 people in wait-list. I am sorry if I understand wrong, but why shouldn't the top 52 people in the wait-list get added to the class?

Thank you so much!
history.subject: Why am I still wailisted for cs170?
